title: Futuristic Robots & Timeless Farts with Brian "Q" Quinn | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 70
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
Chrissy D is out sick this week babes!!!! Sal is joined by Q aka Brain Quinn from Impractical Jokers. The babes talk the future of robots and how it could impact all our lives. We also explore why in fact farts are such a timeless force that unites us all! YASSSS!
